{"tid":1604944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非新職業]有冇人可以mon住所有傷者/被補手足去向","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:33:15.000Z","uid":199012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6678bd57256b0ed005066410aaef82de3af0660d","tid":1604944,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"成日見到有手足重傷但係無辦法知道佢地係生係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連有冇送院都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年烏革都係咁, 佢哋會有人權組織同NGO去track同monitor所有被捕嘅人嘅去向。<br />\n<br />\n要做嘅野好基本就可以<br />\n1. 影相<br />\n2. track救護車/狗車<br />\n3. 整合<br />\n<br />\n唔想再有手足喺海度浮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8725a2447394eeca478cd47528cfe0f975a241","tid":1604944,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"[尋人] 無知覺＋失禁果個無送到醫院<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603272</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f33cd0544ccc33b041e79e5845201e8a6e24b1f0","tid":1604944,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:33:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00fac5ab7b0df8c5f8ce985309e28900aeb02626","tid":1604944,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:33:15.000Z","msg":"push"}]}